      "content": "A coastal village where the harbour charges a toll to enter the marina.\n\nThis tutorial demonstrates **Payment events** — Lightning-gated progression using LNURL.\n\n> **Note:** The LNURL in this tutorial is a placeholder. Payment will not process without a real LNURL endpoint configured."
